        <item>
            <title>1.8.4</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 08:28:07 +0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>66</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.8.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>What's New in 1.8.4</h2><ul></ul><p><strong>Improved</strong></p><ul><li>⚡ Improved BYOK saving, provider switching, and sync reliability across supported AI providers</li><li>🧭 Updated Settings to a more native macOS split-view navigation with cleaner toolbar behavior</li><li>🔄 Improved monitor, hotkey, and AI Rename coordination to reduce duplicate or stuck processing</li></ul><p><strong>Fixed</strong></p><ul><li>🐛 Fixed BYOK requests using out-of-sync provider state during analysis</li><li>🩹 Fixed Restore Purchases so local PRO entitlement refreshes more reliably</li><li>🔧 Fixed Groq timeout and fallback handling for faster recovery from provider stalls</li><li>🛡️ Fixed migration and network-monitor edge cases that could leave app state inconsistent</li></ul>
]]></description>
